        {
          "insert": " validates the complete document envelope and graph rather than isolated blocks. It rejects mismatched map keys and ids, missing roots, orphan references, shared children, cycles, and unreachable blocks. Reads remain tolerant of component-prop drift, and unknown string block types canonicalize to callouts while preserving their former type as "
